## FALLBACK\_PALETTE variable

Fallback ANSI 16-color palette used when terminal color probing is not available. These values are based on common terminal defaults.

**Signature:**

```typescript
FALLBACK_PALETTE: Record<AnsiColorName, RGB>
```
